{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadioItem"}]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Layouts","anchor":"Layouts"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"reversed"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing radio indicator and a leading optional decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Indicator states","anchor":"Indicator-states"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The radio indicator has two available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": the radio is filled with a filled circle, the user has made the action to select the radio"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the radio is empty, does not contain anything, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the radio"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as disabled.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The radio can be also outlined in some cases.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and optional texts and a custom radio trait.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","text":"Forbidden by design","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"can be used outside a dedicated picker, thus it does not need any tag and associated type.","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, and an additional label but without text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", extraLabel: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading radio with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", extraLabel: \"The Beatles\", description: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing radio with a label, a description, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection,","                  label: \"Rescue from this world!\",","                  description: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                  isReversed: true,","                  isError: true,","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection,","                  label: \"Rescue from this world!\",","                  isError: true,","                  errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading radio with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Rescue from this world!\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related radio as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Kaboom!\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection, label: \"Kaboom!\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to flip your icon depending to the layout direction or not (e.g. if RTL mode lose semantics  \/ meanings):","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSRadioItem(isOn: $selection,","                  labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                  flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                  isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-radio-button","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering","level":2},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","text":"Orange Business Tools","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_OrangeBusinessTools","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh","text":"Sosh","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioItem_Wireframe","type":"image"}]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Version","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}]}]}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some radios components."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a radio with only an indicator, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradioitem"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"title":"OUDSRadioItem","symbolKind":"struct","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadioItem","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents13OUDSRadioItemV","platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"15.0"},{"introducedAt":"15.0","beta":false,"name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false},{"introducedAt":"16.0","beta":false,"name":"tvOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false},{"introducedAt":"1.0","beta":false,"name":"visionOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false},{"introducedAt":"11.0","beta":false,"name":"watchOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false}],"roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadioItem"}]},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documenta